oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Freeman home
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Interior view of the living room in the Freeman home, located in Leoma, Tennessee. A. Freeman and Mary Jane McDougal Freeman are seated in rocking chairs by a fireplace with a young boy sitting beside them. The photograph was taken on their 66th wedding anniversary.
